examples.en: The cost was a staggering $10 million.
The amount of money required was staggering.
The enormity of such an act of generosity is staggering.
The storm caused a staggering amount of damage.
Overseas debt is a staggering 16 billion.
The financial impact on the town was staggering.
The streets are full of people staggering home when the area's numerous gin mills close.
the staggering scope of the new construction on campus
